heading: Select a Provider
subheading: Choose the provider you want to talk to in a video, audio or text consultation. It can sometimes take time to find a provider that is a good fit for your needs and your preferred approach.
modal_coupon_heading: Enter your coupon to use it
heading_with_coupon: Select a  Provider to use Coupon: {{coupon}}
coupon_paragraph: Coupons provide “no-cost” sessions and are sponsored by our partners.
coupon_paragraph_two: If you received a coupon code from a social media campaign or a partner, please copy and paste that below. After you submit the coupon code, you will see any providers that support it and their availability. A coupon may support one or more sessions. The platform will indicate if the coupon has expired or reached the maximum session usage.
